OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772827865
OL,3,CPensioner accused over taxi driver
OL,4,Cshooting nearly 20 years ago
OL,6,FA judge has set a preliminary trial
OL,7,Fdate for this November in the case of
OL,8,Fa 76-year-old man charged with the
OL,9,Fmurder of a father-of-four from the
OL,10,FBlack Country, which happened nearly
OL,11,Ftwenty years ago.
OL,13,FHarun Khan, 39, a taxi driver, was
OL,14,Fshot outside his home in Tudor Street
OL,15,Fin Tipton, at 9.25pm on 3rd March 2008.
OL,17,FHe was taken to hospital but was
OL,18,Fpronounced dead a short time later.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
