OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772827865
OL,3,CPensioner accused over taxi driver
OL,4,Cshooting nearly 20 years ago
OL,6,FDavid Harrison from Bilston was
OL,7,Fcharged with murder in connection with
OL,8,Fthe death of Mr Khan, in December 2025.
OL,10,FHe was also charged with wounding with
OL,11,Fintent to cause grievous bodily harm
OL,12,Fin connection with the shooting of a
OL,13,F27-year-old man in Farthings Lane in
OL,14,FDudley, on December 14th 2007.
OL,16,FHe also faces two counts of possessing
OL,17,Fa firearm.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
