CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772827865
OL,3,CPensioner accused over taxi driver
OL,4,Cshooting nearly 20 years ago
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHarrison is currently on remand at HMP
OL,12,FFrankland in County Durham.
OL,14,FHe chose not to appear by video link
OL,15,Ffor a hearing at Wolverhampton Crown
OL,16,FCourt today (6th March).
OL,18,FJudge Michael Chambers KC adjourned
OL,19,Fthe case and set a preliminary trial
OL,20,Fdate of November 16th.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772827865
OL,3,CPensioner accused over taxi driver
OL,4,Cshooting nearly 20 years ago
OL,6,FThe trial is expected to last three
OL,7,Fweeks.
OL,9,FThe judge said of Harrison's absence
OL,10,Ffrom the hearing:
OL,12,F"The simple course is that a not
OL,13,Fguilty plea be entered but given the
OL,14,Fseriousness of the case I think I
OL,15,Fought to give the defence an
OL,16,Fopportunity to try and see Mr Harrison.
OL,18,F"The case stands adjourned and the
OL,19,Fdefendant remains in custody in
OL,20,Frelation to this matter."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
